OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUS price rises ease for the
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffirst time in months       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The pace of price increases in the US  
OL,6, eased slightly in April, as costs for  
OL,7, petrol, used cars and clothing slipped.
OL,9,FThe annual pace of inflation was 8.3%  
OL,10,Flast month, down from 8.5% in March,   
OL,11,Fthe Labor Department said.             
OL,13,FThat marked the first decline in months
OL,14,Fbut the rate of price increases        
OL,15,Fremained at a 40-year high.            
OL,17,FThe cost of groceries, housing and     
OL,18,Fitems like airline tickets continued to
OL,19,Frise, putting pressure on policymakers 
OL,20,Fto rein in the increases.              
